REACTION   (24-CR-52(D,P)24-CR-53,PAR,DA)
STATUS     (TABLE,,M.Spieker+,J,PR/C,112,064331,2025) Figs. 6-9
           Data were provided by M.Spieker on March 2, 2026.
ENDBIB               3
